    <div class="terms_and_conditions"><p >
      <h1 style="text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">GENERAL TERMS AND CONDITIONS</h1>
      <ul class="terms">
        <ul>
<li>Car rental bookings should be made 24 hours prior to travel.</li>
<li>INR rates are applicable to all resident Indians.</li>
<li>Dollar rates are applicable to foreign nationals and NRIs settling their bills directly even if hosted by an Indian individual or an establishment.</li>
<li>Car rental will be charged with the car rental office as the start and end point.</li>
<li>A fraction of an hour will be charged as one hour.</li>
<li>A fraction of a kilometer will be charged as one kilometer.</li>
<li>Interstate taxes, permit fees, parking fees, toll taxes, etc. are to be paid by the customer on actuals.</li>
<li>Car rental tariffs are subject to change without prior notice.</li>
<li>Express Travel Corporation liability is limited to refund of the amount of rental charged against the particular transaction.</li>
<li>All cars are comprehensively insured including 3rd party cover. Claims if any will be settled as per existing laws in India<br> by the concerned insurance company.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">CANCELLATION CHARGES FOR RESERVATION</h3>
<ul>
<li>Cancellations 24 hours prior to pick up will attract cancellation charges equivalent to 25% of the gross price.</li>
<li>Cancellation 6 hours prior to pick up will attract cancellation charges equivalent to the full amount for one day.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">CHAUFFEUR DRIVE- LOCAL USE</h3>
<ul>
<li>If extra hours are logged, the next package rate with extra hours and kilometers will be charged as applicable.</li>
<li>A daily night halt charge (between INR 150 and INR 500 depending on the model of car) will be payable if the car rental<br> package timings have been completed and the car has been retained beyond 24:00 hours.</li>
<li>Driver charges are applicable if the car travels beyond city / corporation limits.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">CHAUFFEUR DRIVE-OUTSTATION USE</h3>
<ul>
<li>Minimum billing of 225 km per calendar day applicable.</li>
<li>Rate per km will be charged as mentioned in the extra km column.</li>
<li>Driver charges (between INR 200 and INR 500) are payable on a daily basis.</li>
<li>All inter-state permits, fees, taxes, etc., will be charged on actuals.</li>
<li>In hilly areas, charges per kilometer & driver's charges will be 50% extra.</li>
<li>Credit Card: The Hirer must have a valid credit card in their own name.</li>
<li>Master/VISA/credit cards are accepted.</li>
<li>On commencement of rental, a blank signed credit card imprint will be taken.</li>
<li>All charges pertaning to the rental including extra days, optional items, delivery and collection, one-way rates, tolls,<br> damage and repair costs if any, driving, parking or traffic fines, taxes etc.</li>
<li>will be charged to the credit card.</li>

<li>Insurance: All vehicles are comprehensively insured under a motor car insurance policy.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">PAYMENT TERMS</h3>
<ul>
<li>Advance payment will be made to Express Travel Corporation for the car rental unless there is a written contract and the<br> credit terms have been approved by the company in writing.</li>
<li>Credit terms can be reviewed by the company at any time at its sole discretion.</li>
<li>In some cases the customer may be requested to pay the service provider directly.</li>
<li>A 12.24% service tax will be charged on the total billing amount based on the Government.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
